Package: trendMoMo
Type: Package
Title: Prototype Trend Extensions to StMoMo
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Description: Prototype extension to the Stochastic Mortality Modelling (StMoMo) framework
    that adds baseline linear improvement rates and broken-trend components
    at user-specified calendar years. Includes identifiability constraint handlers,
    coefficient extraction, and plotting helpers. This is research code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    stats,
    graphics,
    utils,
    methods,
    StMoMo
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/amvillegas/trendMoMo
BugReports: https://github.com/amvillegas/trendMoMo/issues
